name: vinn
review_text:
I come from Canada and have worked in fast food places, where speed is prioritized. I was shocked at how long it took for the food to come out (over 10 minutes) since there weren't many customers and only one delivery pickup person within over a half hour.

Before ordering, I needed to ask a worker a question at the till and they walked past me multiple times for 5 minutes before someone addressed me. One worker was just stocking ketchup packets instead of helping me.

One of our burgers was very lopsided. Bathroom was clean but women's stall had no soap.

name: Cristina Catala
review_text:
Me parece vergonzoso por parte del encargado de esta sucursal poner solo a 2 empleados que tenian que preparar los menus del momento,la caja y los pedidos on line.? Que pasa que la cadena no tiene dinero? A los pobres chicos no les daba la vida.Encima recoje mesas( fatal por parte de los usuarios) y limpia.
El local es super centrico delante de un hospital,no arriba de los pirineos
review_translated_text:
I find it shameful that the manager of this branch only had two employees who were supposed to prepare the menus, run the register, and take online orders. name: rolando choque
review_text:
Era un martes por la tarde y Jorge, cansado de su jornada, decidio premiarse con una Big Mac
. Entro al McDonald's del barrio, pidio su combo y se sento tranquilamente en una mesa cerca de la ventana.

Todo iba bien hasta que entro un payaso.
Literalmente, un payaso. Nariz roja, peluca multicolor, zapatotes y todo.
Se llamaba "Globito" (lo decia en su camiseta). Lo curioso es que nadie lo habia contratado.

El payaso fue directo al mostrador y dijo con voz solemne:

--"Una Cajita Feliz... para mi. Porque me lo merezco."

La chica de la caja lo miro un segundo y luego, sin inmutarse, le pregunto:

--"?Con juguete de dinosaurio o de princesas?"

--"Princesas, obviamente. Son mas poderosas", respondio Globito, ofendido.

Se sento justo frente a Jorge. Sin decir nada, saco un globo, lo inflo con fuerza y empezo a hacer una figura.
Jorge, incomodo pero curioso, lo miraba de reojo mientras daba otro mordisco a su hamburguesa.

Finalmente, el payaso termino y le entrego el globo a Jorge:

--"Toma. Es un dragon... o un perro... bueno, algo con forma."

Jorge se rio. Globito tambien. Luego ambos se dieron cuenta de que sin querer habian mordido la misma papa frita del centro de la bandeja.

No volvieron a hablar.

Pero Jorge todavia guarda ese globo en su coche.
review_translated_text:
It was a Tuesday afternoon, and Jorge, tired of his day, decided to reward himself with a Big Mac.

He walked into the local McDonald's, ordered his combo, and sat quietly at a table near the window.

Everything was going well until a clown walked in.
Literally, a clown. Red nose, multicolored wig, big shoes, and everything.
His name was "Ballon" (it said so on his T-shirt). The funny thing is, no one had hired him.

The clown went straight to the counter and said in a solemn voice:

"A Happy Meal... for me. Because I deserve it."

The girl at the register looked at him for a second and then, without flinching, asked:

"With a dinosaur toy or a princess toy?"

"Princesses, obviously. They're more powerful," Ballon replied, offended.

He sat right in front of Jorge. Without saying anything, he took out a balloon, blew it up hard, and began to make a shape.

Jorge, uncomfortable but curious, looked at him out of the corner of his eye as he took another bite of his hamburger.

Finally, the clown finished and handed the balloon to Jorge:

"Here. It's a dragon... or a dog... well, something shaped."

Jorge laughed. Balloon too. Then they both realized they had accidentally bitten into the same French fry from the center of the tray.

They didn't speak again.

But Jorge still keeps that balloon in his car.

review_translated_text: This morning I went for lunch with my children and the staff were very attentive. They brought our order to the table, provided a highchair for my baby, and were very kind to us. The restaurant was very clean and the service was excellent. We'll be back!
response_from_owner_text: !Hola Antonella! Desde McDonald's agradecemos tu puntuacion y que nos hayas elegido. !Esperamos verte de vuelta por nuestro restaurante!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Hello Antonella! We at McDonald's appreciate your rating and your choice. We hope to see you back at our restaurant!

name: Foodlokibcn
review_text: El restaurante estaba bastante sucio con mesas llena de bandejas pero estaba lleno de gente y es normal no se puede atender y limpiar a la vez. Una pena que los clientes no sean limpios. El menu infantil no estaba mal lo unico las patatas estaban frias y habian perdido el sabor. Los nuggets estaban calientes y crujientes.
review_translated_text: The restaurant was quite dirty, with tables littered with trays, but it was packed, so it's understandable; you can't serve customers and clean at the same time. It's a shame the customers aren't clean. The kids' menu wasn't bad, except the fries were cold and had lost their flavor. The nuggets were hot and crispy.
response_from_owner_text: Agradecemos tu comentario Foodlokibcn, en McDonald's intentamos ofrecer una atencion personalizada a nuestros clientes para que la experiencia sea lo mejor posible. !Que pases un buen dia!
response_from_owner_translated_text: We appreciate your comment, Foodlokibcn. At McDonald's, we strive to offer personalized service to our customers to ensure the best possible experience. Have a great day!

review_text: Late evening shift (10.02) was working non stop, from the moment I walked in till the moment I finished my meal. Manager/Owner please consider adding more people to help, then you will not have bad reviews regarding waiting time and tidiness of the location.

name: Lulu Rocio
review_text: Fui a pedir comida para llevar y no habia mucha gente. Pude ver que mi comida estaba lista a los 10 minutos, pero la chica que atendia se la pasaba coqueteando con su companero y tuve que esperar 5 minutos mas. Pedi salsas y la chica no me dio ninguna. Las patatas frias (eso lo entiendo porque era tarde) pero insipidas porque no le pusieron ni pizca de sal. Muy decepcionante, porque solia ser un buen sitio con servicio decente.
review_translated_text: I went to get takeout, and there weren't many people there. I could see my food was ready in 10 minutes, but the waiter kept flirting with her colleague, and I had to wait another 5 minutes. I asked for sauces, but the waiter didn't give me any. The chips were cold (I understand because it was late), but they were bland because they didn't add a bit of salt. Very disappointing, because it used to be a good place with decent service.
response_from_owner_text: Gracias por tu feedback Lulu, nos ayuda a mejorar nuestros restaurantes. Te esperamos de nuevo en McDonald's.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you for your feedback, Lulu. It helps us improve our restaurants. We look forward to seeing you again at McDonald's.

name: Aaron Jenaghi Marin
review_text:
Los nuggets en este McDonalds en especifico son incomestibles.

He comido nuggets en muchos McDonalds y en ninguno estan hechos de esta forma, esta es la segunda vez que pido nuggets aqui este ano y el rebozado esta suequisimo y con un sabor y textura horrorosos, no se por que, supongo que no los cocinan en la freidora o que los queman.

No se acaba de apreciar en las fotografias pero el rebozado esta seco incluso a simple vista, y como ya he dicho el sabor y la textura son pesimos, nada que ver con el resto de McDonalds en los que he comido este ano.

Por desgracia esta es la segunda vez que tengo que tirar los nuggets a la basura porque literalmente no se pueden comer.
review_translated_text:
The nuggets at this particular McDonald's are inedible.

I've eaten nuggets at many McDonald's, and none of them are made this way. This is the second time I've ordered nuggets here this year, and the coating is incredibly dry and has a horrible taste and texture. I don't know why; I suppose they don't cook them in the fryer or they burn them.

It's hard to see in the photos, but the coating is dry even to the naked eye, and as I've already said, the taste and texture are terrible, nothing like the other McDonald's I've eaten at this year.

Unfortunately, this is the second time I've had to throw the nuggets away because they are literally inedible.
response_from_owner_text: !Hola Aaron! Te agradecemos tus palabras, para ayudarnos a seguir mejorando puedes contarnos mas detalles en atencionconsumidor@es.mcd.com. !Gracias!

name: Alejandro Marchador
review_text:
Hay cosas tolerables y otras que no y esta es precisamente de las que no...
Lo que no puede ser es que yo pida un menu, lo haga grande el cual incluyen la bebida y las patatas y me pongan esa racion tan insignificante con 10 patatas literalmente... pero lo peor de lo peor es que pague una racion de 5EU de patatas con bacon y queso y me den, como podeis ver, una bandeja algo mas grande que la individual y casi casi hayan las mismas patatas esparcidas pareciendo que hay mas cuando se ve de sobras que ESA BASURA no vale 5EU.
Verguenza, se os deberia caer la cara de verguenza a este establecimiento por, literalmente, timar a los clientes de esta manera con esas raciones.
Y direis, porque no te has quejado?
Porque si me quejo, solo me lo hacen a mi, pero si lo publico aqui, la cosa cambia.
Mejorad mas este establecimiento y hacer que los trabajadores presten mas atencion a los pedidos y dejen de hablar entre ellos.
review_translated_text:
There are things that are tolerable and others that aren't, and this is precisely one of those that aren't...
What's unacceptable is that I order a menu, make it large, which includes a drink and fries, and they give me this insignificant portion with literally 10 fries... but the worst of the worst is that I paid for a EU5 portion of fries with bacon and cheese, and they give me, as you can see, a tray slightly larger than the individual one, and they almost have the same number of fries scattered around, making it seem like there are more when it's clear that THIS TRASH isn't worth EU5.
Shame on you! This establishment should be ashamed of itself for literally ripping off customers like this with those portions.
And you might say, "Why haven't you complained?"
Because if I complain, it's only me who gets it, but if I publish it here, things will change.
Improve this establishment more and make the workers pay more attention to orders and stop talking to each other.

name: Irene Marin
review_text: La verdad es que hacia tiempo que no comia Mcdonald's y me lleve una gran decepcion por la perdida de calidad. Una bicmac realmente seca, poca variedad de salsas para los nuggets y bastante tardanza por la impresionante cantidad de pedidos a domicilio.
review_translated_text: The truth is, I hadn't eaten at McDonald's in a while, and I was deeply disappointed by the loss of quality. The Bicmac was really dry, there was little variety in the sauces for the nuggets, and it took a while to arrive due to the overwhelming number of delivery orders.
response_from_owner_text: Lamentamos tu experiencia, en McDonald's nos esforzamos por ofrecer un servicio correcto y quee todo este a gusto de nuestros clientes, esperamos que la proxima vez la experiencia sea mucho mejor.
response_from_owner_translated_text: We're sorry for your experience. At McDonald's, we strive to provide excellent service and ensure our customers are satisfied. We hope the experience will be even better next time.

name: Elemento
review_text: Lamentable trato por parte de la chica de gafas morena grandota. 2 hamburguesas y patatas para llevar y solo me da un sobre de ketchup en la bolsa, le pido otro y mostaza y me contesta con mala cara y de malas maneras que no se puede dar mas. Increible!! Ya no me atrevi a pedir una bolsa de asas. No creo que les sobren los clientes para tratarlos asi.
review_translated_text: Terrible treatment from the big, brunette girl with glasses. Two burgers and fries to go, and she only gives me a packet of ketchup in the bag. I ask for another one and mustard, and she tells me with a snarky and rude face that she can't give me more. Incredible!! I didn't dare ask for a tote bag anymore. I don't think they have enough customers to treat them like that.
response_from_owner_text: Gracias por visitarnos Elemento, en McDonalds procuramos cuidar cada detalle para que este a gusto de nuestros clientes y ofrecer una atencion personalizada, estudiaremos lo ocurrido. !Esperamos que vuelvas pronto!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you for visiting Elemento. At McDonald's, we strive to take care of every detail to ensure our customers' satisfaction and offer personalized service. We will investigate what happened. We hope you'll come back soon!

name: RD Garcia
review_text:
Hemos venido dos veces porque estamos en el clinic, y las dos veces se han equivocado todo para menos, faltaba una hamburguesa, en la cbo no llevaba el beicon, en la doble le faltaba una hamburguesa.
Entiendo que esten aprendiendo y la voluntad sea buena pero la queja se la pongo al dueno de la franquicia por no estar ahi haciendo formacion y seguimiento hacia sus empleados.
review_translated_text:
We've come twice because we're at the clinic, and both times they've made mistakes, all of them worse. One burger was missing, the combo burger didn't have bacon, and the double burger was missing a patty.

I understand they're learning and their intentions are good, but my complaint is directed at the franchise owner for not being there to train and supervise his employees.
response_from_owner_text: Sentimos la experiencia RD, en McDonald's trabajamos a diario por servir comida de calidad, nos esforzaremos para que la experiencia mejore en la proxima visita.
response_from_owner_translated_text: We are sorry for the RD experience. At McDonald's, we work daily to serve quality food, and we will strive to make the experience even better on your next visit.

review_translated_text:
It looked like a typical Mac, but the staff's attitude immediately displeased me. I ordered the usual menu (Coke Zero, fries, a triple cheeseburger, and Oreo ice cream).
The burger was poorly packaged, and the bun was undercooked with white streaks (I hope it was just undercooked).
The temperature in the building was also really bad: it was hot and stuffy on the first floor, and freezing on the second.
And most importantly, the restroom was filthy--I was shocked.

Tambien ofrecemos una amplia variedad de desayunos McBreakfast, asi como un espacio McCafe en el que podras relajarte, disfrutar de un cafe y mucho mas. Te esperamos!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thanks for visiting, Briii! At McDonald's, we don't just want you to think of us when you're looking for lunch or dinner in Barcelona. We also offer a wide variety of McBreakfast options, as well as a McCafe where you can relax, enjoy a coffee, and much more. We look forward to seeing you!

name: Pol Allue-Creus Pedemonte
review_text: Muy lentos. Vine porque tenia prisa y desde que hice el pedido hasta que me lo dieron paso mas de media hora. Mas q fast food, very slow food. El suelo encharcado de coca cola y nadie limpiandolo, cada vez mas repartido por las pisadas de la gente... un desastre. El peor mcdonalds en el que he estado nunca.
review_translated_text: Very slow. I came because I was in a hurry, and it took more than half an hour from when I placed my order until I received it. More than fast food, it's very slow food. The floor was soaked with Coca-Cola and nobody was cleaning it, and it was getting more and more spread by people's footsteps... a disaster. The worst McDonald's I've ever been to.
response_from_owner_text: !Hola Pol! Lamentamos que tu experiencia no haya sido positiva, tenemos en cuenta tu opinion para que podamos seguir mejorando. Saludos.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Hi Pol! We're sorry your experience wasn't positive. We'll take your feedback into account so we can continue to improve. Best regards.

name: Irvin Systems
review_text: Me gusto mucho la atencion, es un lugar muy agradable, sobre todo el personal de caja, y todo sale muy rapido cuando haces un pedido en la maquina. saludos
review_translated_text: I really liked the service. It's a very pleasant place, especially the checkout staff. Everything comes out very quickly when you place an order at the machine. Best regards.
response_from_owner_text: Gracias Irvin por tomarte el tiempo para dejarnos un comentario, en McDonald's trabajamos por ofrecer un servicio de 10. !Saludos!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you Irvin for taking the time to leave us a comment. At McDonald's, we strive to offer top-notch service. Best regards!

name: SYED ABID HUSSAIN SHAH
response_from_owner_text: SYED estamos encantados de que McDonald's sea tu restaurante de referencia en Barcelona. Contamos con una gran variedad de McMenus, asi como del Happy Meal, un menu divertido y equilibrado, no solo para los mas pequenos de la casa.
response_from_owner_translated_text: SYED is delighted that McDonald's is your go-to restaurant in Barcelona. We offer a wide variety of McMenus, as well as the Happy Meal, a fun and balanced meal, not just for the little ones.

name: Adelio Settimi
review_text: Veloci e gentili.ambiente tranquillo
review_translated_text: Fast and friendly. Quiet environment.
response_from_owner_text: !Gracias por tu review Adelio! En McDonald's queremos que puedas disfrutar de nuestras hamburguesas como te mereces, por eso en nuestros restaurantes solo encontraras carne fresca 100% vacuno espanol, procedente de granjas comprometidas con el bienestar animal.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thanks for your review, Adelio! At McDonald's, we want you to enjoy our burgers the way you deserve, which is why in our restaurants you'll only find 100% fresh Spanish beef, sourced from farms committed to animal welfare.

name: Richard P
review_text: McDonald's e ormai alla frutta, qualitativamente il cibo e pessimo, porzioni piccole e care. Mai piu.
review_translated_text: McDonald's is now on the rocks. The food quality is terrible, portions are small, and it's expensive. Never again.
response_from_owner_text: Lamentamos que tu experiencia no haya sido positiva, trasladamos tu feedback a nuestro departamento de calidad para que podamos seguir mejorando. Saludos.
response_from_owner_translated_text: We regret that your experience was not positive. We have forwarded your feedback to our quality department so that we can continue to improve. Regards.

name: Pablo Ortiz
review_text: Excelente atencion y mobiliario muy moderno.
review_translated_text: Excellent service and very modern furniture.
response_from_owner_text: Gracias por tu visita a nuestro restaurante McDonald's de Barcelona , trabajamos para que todo este a gusto de nuestros clientes. !Esperamos verte pronto de nuevo!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you for visiting our McDonald's restaurant in Barcelona. We work hard to ensure our customers' satisfaction. We hope to see you again soon!

name: Alex Aragon
response_from_owner_text: !Hola Alex! gracias por tu comentario, en McDonald's los tenemos muy en cuenta para mejorar. !Que pases un buen dia!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Hi Alex! Thanks for your feedback. At McDonald's, we take your comments into account to help us improve. Have a great day!

name: JAN ix
response_from_owner_text: Gracias por visitarnos JAN. En McDonald's no solo queremos que pienses en nosotros cuando quieras comer o cenar en Barcelona. Tambien ofrecemos una amplia variedad de desayunos McBreakfast, asi como un espacio McCafe en el que podras relajarte, disfrutar de un cafe y mucho mas. Te esperamos!
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you for visiting, Jan. At McDonald's, we don't just want you to think of us when you want to eat lunch or dinner in Barcelona. We also offer a wide variety of McBreakfast options, as well as a McCafe where you can relax, enjoy a coffee, and much more. We look forward to seeing you!

name: Enric Gonzalez Lorenzo
review_text: Esta Franquicia nunca defrauda. Buenos productos y precios rompedores. Si te gusta el Fast Food, este es un lugar de referencia
review_translated_text: This franchise never disappoints. Great products and unbeatable prices. If you like fast food, this is a must-visit!

name: JORDI ROMEU i PALOP
review_text: M'agrada aquest McDonald's. Esta bastant net, les empleades son amables i tenen wi-fi. Ben situat davant de l'hospital Clinic. Ha millorat molt el servei i el tracte de les empleades amb la clientela. L'unica pega es que no tenen l'espai infantil.
review_translated_text: I like this McDonald's. It's pretty clean, the employees are friendly and they have wi-fi. It's well located in front of the Clinic hospital. The service and the way the employees treat their customers has improved a lot. The only downside is that they don't have a children's area.

name: anli F
review_text: mcspicy good

name: Hussan Juel
review_text: Good place

name: Victor Reigosa
review_text: Un big mac que no es big mac
review_translated_text: A Big Mac that isn't a Big Mac

name: xingjin liu
review_text: Muy lento, mucho ruido, los trabajadores estan jugando, mal ambiente.
review_translated_text: Very slow, very noisy, workers are playing, bad atmosphere.

name: Aida Forero
review_text: Un lugar amplio para estar con amigos y despartir
review_translated_text: A spacious place to be with friends and have a good time

name: Gemma S
review_text: Entiendo que te confundas con una cosa, pero ponerlo todo mal no. Parece que sea a proposito ya que era para llevar y no vamos a volver para que la cambien. Era sin lechuga y sin salsa la hamburguesa, pongo las fotos:
review_translated_text: I understand you might be confused about one thing, but getting everything wrong is unacceptable. It seems like it was done on purpose since it was a takeout order and we're not going back to have it replaced. The burger had no lettuce and no sauce. I've attached photos:

name: Pedro Redondo
review_text:
Me han puesto un cuarto de libra sin el pan de arriba hay que ser tontos y en las patatas habia trozos de servilleta. Que asco da este mcdonals.

Ademas, La higiene muy justita. Los empleados cogen las patatas en lugar de por la bolsa por arriba sin guantes y sin limpiarse las manos despues de tocar la caja u otras cosas
review_translated_text:
They gave me a Quarter Pounder without the top bun--how stupid! And there were pieces of napkin in the fries. This McDonald's is disgusting.

Also, the hygiene is terrible. The employees grab the fries from the top of the bag instead of the bag, without gloves and without cleaning their hands after touching the box or anything else.

name: Pere rovira bertran
review_text: Esperant mes de 10' un mini-McFlurry, oblida't per despiste i a la entrega 40% aigualit.
review_translated_text: Waiting more than 10 minutes for a mini-McFlurry, forget it due to carelessness and upon delivery it is 40% watered down.

name: Esteve L.
review_text: Obligatorio pasar por la maquina si quieres comer algo, y intenta no equivocarte, yo me equivoque y hice mi pedido para llevar y me lo estuvieron recordando."es que usted a puesto para llevar" cuando yo queria consumir en el local.
review_translated_text: You must go through the vending machine if you want to eat something, and try not to make a mistake. I made a mistake and placed my order for takeout, and they kept reminding me, "You've set it to takeout," when I wanted to eat in.

name: Montserrat Jimenez Guillomet
review_text: Esta muy concurrido , pero muy bien.
review_translated_text: It's very crowded, but very good.

name: Ventura
review_text: Only coffe. Good

name: javier petit
review_text: La atencion es muy lenta es todo
review_translated_text: The service is very slow, that's all.

name: Stefan Hadorn
review_text: War gut und sauber
review_translated_text: It was good and clean

name: Edson Mesquita
review_text: La comida es Mac, pero no visitar el domingo por la noche, es como comer sobras ... Las mesas muy sucias, el staff poco simpatico... solo recomienda se quieres amargurte el resto del dia...
review_translated_text: The food is good, but don't go on Sunday night; it's like eating leftovers. The tables are very dirty, the staff unfriendly... I only recommend it if you want to ruin the rest of your day.

name: Notsunodai
review_text: Como toda los MacDonalds, pero si estas en hora de merienda o algo similar va tardar un poco mas que lo normal,pero de puede justificar por que tiene bastante escuelas a lado y un hospital con muchos estudiantes de medico y respetables trabajadores sanitarios
review_translated_text: Like all McDonald's, but if you are at snack time or something similar it will take a little longer than usual, but it can be justified because it has many schools nearby and a hospital with many medical students and respectable health workers.

name: Francisco Javier Lopez Salmeron
review_text: Reliable food chain franchisee. Specialised in serving the food quickly.

name: Majed Hossain
review_text: Very fast.  I love it

name: El tiempo de Dios es perfecto
review_text: El lugar esta muy bien, mi pedido no a tardado nada en prepararlo....lo que no me gusto que me preparo mi pedido en una bandeja sucia pienso con lo estamos viviendo ahora con este virus tendrian que tener mas cuidado!
review_translated_text: The place is very nice, my order was prepared very quickly... what I didn't like was that they prepared my order on a dirty tray. I think with everything we're going through now with this virus, they should be more careful!

name: Yosy Boomers
review_text: Excelente Ruco, rico, rico ah
review_translated_text: Excellent Ruco, delicious, delicious ah

name: Alejandro Cervantes Conesa
review_text:
Este McDonald es vergonzoso! No hay dia que pidamos y lo traigan como lo queremos y pagamos claro.
Hacen los mcflurry a su antojo, de los topping que se les antoja y sin tener en cuenta los extra que pagas. No contentos con eso, llamas y si tienes suerte de que lo cojan, explicas lo que pasa y te cuelgan. VENGONZOSO
review_translated_text:
This McDonald's is shameful! Not a day goes by when we order and they bring it just the way we want it, and we pay, of course.
They make the McFlurry any way they want, with whatever toppings they want, and they don't take into account the extras you pay. Not content with that, you call, and if you're lucky enough to get picked up, you explain what's going on, and they hang up on you. VENGEANT

name: Guillermo O. Musante
review_text: Local chico de mc Donald, pero bien servicio de cafeteria !!!
review_translated_text: Small McDonald's, but good cafeteria service!!!

name: marina balius
review_text: Habia tenido muchos problemas con este McDonalds hasta que me ha atendido una chica que se llamaba Natalia. Me ha escuchado, ha entendido mi preocupacion para que no me llevara un producto con ingredientes de los que tengo alergia, ha sido servicial y muy educada. Incluso se ha ofrecido para llamarme en cuanto tuviera el pedido para poder atender mejor mi peticion. Por gente como ella gato un dinero gustosamente. Gracias Natalia por ser una de las pocas trabajadoras que me ha atendido asi.
review_translated_text: I'd had a lot of problems with this McDonald's until a girl named Natalia served me. She listened to me, understood my concern about not ordering something with ingredients I'm allergic to, and was helpful and very polite. She even offered to call me as soon as my order was ready so she could better address my request. It's because of people like her that I gladly spend money. Thank you, Natalia, for being one of the few employees who has treated me like this.

name: Jean Carlos Loza Espinoza
review_text: Distribucion rara pero muy tranquilo
review_translated_text: Strange layout but very quiet

name: Gabriel Angel Beldad Garcia
review_text: Perfecto , mas tranquilo que otros , al menos en Domingo y un buen servicio
review_translated_text: Perfect, quieter than others, at least on Sundays, and good service.

name: jenifer duarte
review_text: La comida no estaba tan buena, no tenia el sabor caracteristico de la cadena:(
review_translated_text: The food wasn't that good, it didn't have the chain's signature flavor :(

name: Ana Risso Solanas Pacheco
review_text: Buena atencion. Rapido sistema de pedidos y expedicion. Un poco caro si llevas ninos.
review_translated_text: Good service. Fast ordering and shipping. A bit pricey if you have children.

name: Isabel Santiago cota das neves
review_text: Como todos los de su genero
review_translated_text: Like all those of its kind

name: Jorge Eduardo Villanueva

review_translated_text: Fast and efficient service. A very good experience.

name: Babacar Fall

review_translated_text: Good place

name: Carmina
review_text: McDonald's cerca de Hospital Clinic de Barcelona
review_translated_text: McDonald's near Hospital Clinic of Barcelona

name: Maria Jose
review_text:
El MacDonalds mas lento que he ido en mi vida.
Aunque no habia gente han tardado un monton en darme el pedido
review_translated_text:
The slowest McDonald's I've ever been to.
Even though there weren't many people there, it took them ages to bring my order.

name: Francisco Reyes (Salomon el Justo)
review_text: No te recomiendo nada este ya que el trato personal no existe el tiempo de entrega de los pedidos es superior a 20 minutos
review_translated_text: I do not recommend this one at all since there is no personal treatment and the delivery time for orders is more than 20 minutes.

name: Yordi
review_text: Como McDonald's de la estacion de Sants ninguno
review_translated_text: There is no McDonald's at Sants station like this one.

name: Umar Nasr
review_text: Good

name: jordi alvarez valles
review_text: Bastante lento para servir
review_translated_text: Quite slow to serve

name: Gy Rem
review_text: Podrian mejorar en hacer mas eficiente el tiempo de entrega de los pedidos, y las bebidas no tenian mucho sabor, parecia mas agua que otra cosa, la ultima vez que estuvimos alli
review_translated_text: They could improve their order delivery time, and the drinks didn't have much flavor; they tasted more like water than anything else, the last time we were there.

name: Angel barba romero
review_text: Las hamburguesas de las ofertas muy baratas pero una carne pequena que no sabe a carne, una cantidad desmesurada de tiras de lechuga para rellenar y no puedes rellenar las bebidas como si se puede en USA que es de donde viene la empresa o como ya sucede en locales de la competencia
review_translated_text: The burgers on offer are very cheap, but the meat is small and tastes nothing like meat, there are an excessive amount of lettuce strips to fill, and you can't refill your drinks like you can in the USA, where the company is from, or like it already happens in competing establishments.

name: Antonieta Carrasquero
review_text: El restaurante es muy tranquilo. Despejado y limpio. Pero Tienen que hacer una mejora radical con la App y el sistema de puntos de fidelizacion del cliente. Haciendo el pedido por la pantalla hemos perdido casi la mitad de nuestros puntos y al final el trabajador del local no pudo aplicarnos el descuento correspondiente  por lo que tuvimos que pagar precios completos y aparte perder los puntos de la app.
review_translated_text: The restaurant is very quiet. Clear and clean. But they need to make radical improvements to the app and the customer loyalty points system. By ordering online, we lost almost half of our points, and in the end, the restaurant employee couldn't apply the corresponding discount, so we had to pay full prices and lose the app points.

name: Yawer Ali
review_text: Aqui sirven hamburguesas frias
review_translated_text: They serve cold burgers here.

name: Marc
review_text: La gerencia de este restaurante deberia prestar atencion a las malas resenas que acumulan, pues no puedo estar mas de acuerdo: vivo cerca y siempre que voy hay errores con el pedido, productos que se entregan frios, largas esperas (ademas en momentos que casi no hay nadie) y habitualmente malas formas por parte del personal, con alguna excepcion. De los peores establecimientos de la cadena en los que he estado.
review_translated_text: The management of this restaurant should pay attention to the bad reviews they've been getting, as I couldn't agree more: I live nearby, and every time I go there, there are mistakes with the order, cold products, long waits (especially at times when there's hardly anyone there), and routinely rude staff, with a few exceptions. One of the worst establishments in the chain I've been to.

name: FRANCISCA BURGUILLOS MORENO
review_text: Excelente atencion al cliente y mucha limpieza en mesas y local en general
review_translated_text: Excellent customer service and very clean tables and the premises in general.

name: Gregory Ramos
review_text: Uff demasiado bueno. Excelente atencion.
review_translated_text: Wow, that's great. Excellent service.

name: antonio rodriguez
review_text: Muy lentos
review_translated_text: Very slow

name: Carlos Yepez
review_text: comida rapida, hamburguesa mal montada
review_translated_text: fast food, poorly assembled hamburger

name: Javier Gonzalez
review_text: Manana atencion
review_translated_text: Tomorrow attention

name: Norberto Fernandez
review_text: Poca gente muy organizados
review_translated_text: Few people, very organized

name: Angela Caraghiosu Filip
review_text: He probodo un menu nuevo de color negro (la caixa), diferente y novedoso.
review_translated_text: I tried a new menu in black (la caixa), different and innovative.

name: Health Life Ever
review_text: Siempre he comido de este McDonald a pesar de muchos errores en los pedidos, pq lo tengo a lado de mi trabajo, pero hoy dia 10/12/2021 no me han dejado entrar por el certificado covid, normal y logico, pero tampoco me han dejado llevar comida, que conste que cuando termine el Covid, jamas volvere a comprar en este McDonald en especial.
review_translated_text: I've always eaten at this McDonald's despite many errors in my orders, because it's right next to my work, but today, December 10, 2021, they wouldn't let me in because of the COVID certificate, which is normal and understandable, but they also wouldn't let me take food to go. Let it be known that when COVID is over, I will never buy from this particular McDonald's again.

name: JORDI
review_text:
No em van demanar el DNI per comprovar que el certificat de vacunacio COVID que jo portava fos el meu.
Molta espera per a que ens donguessin el sopar i pendre'l a l'establiment. Tenen moltes comandes via Globo i donen preferencia a aquestes en detriment dels clients que estan al local.
Males formes i contestacions del personal. Molta feina  per pocs empleats.
review_translated_text:
They didn't ask for my ID to verify that the COVID vaccination certificate I had was mine.
Long wait for dinner to be served and to be served at the establishment. They have many orders via Globo and give priority to these to the detriment of customers who are in the premises.
Bad manners and responses from the staff. A lot of work for few employees.

name: Valentina
review_text: Se demoraron 30 minutos en entregar mi pedido! Una total locura. Las chicas no daban con sus manos para entregar tantos pedidos . Necesitan mas personal! No fue comoda rapida y sobre todo, para la proxima no creo venir a esta sucursal.
review_translated_text: It took them 30 minutes to deliver my order! Absolutely insane. The staff couldn't handle so many orders. They need more staff! It wasn't conveniently fast, and above all, I don't think I'll be coming back to this store next time.

name: Mo Van Horn
review_text: Okay
review_translated_text: OK

name: Marc Royo
review_text: Como todos, la uniformidad es la regla de oro.
review_translated_text: As with everyone, uniformity is the golden rule.

name: Gilberth Marquez
review_text: Muy buenas
review_translated_text: Very good

name: Marc Gali
review_text: No hay una sola vez que consigan entregar un pedido entero para llevar. Cuando no se olvidan las patatas, se olvidan los nuggets,... Ya no hablemos de servilletas, pajita,... Servicio deplorable
review_translated_text: There's not a single time they manage to deliver an entire takeout order. When they don't forget the fries, they forget the nuggets... Not to mention napkins, straws... Deplorable service.

name: victor beneit calomarde
review_text: Bien, mesas sucias
review_translated_text: Okay, dirty tables

name: nsr
review_text: excelente
review_translated_text: excellent

name: Carlitos
review_text: Rico
review_translated_text: Rich

name: MAJID SULTAN
review_text: El codigo de mi orden era 030 mira yo me lo he habia pedido un chiken mayo vale 1,30EU y un cheeseburger que vale 1,40EUyo soy un repartidor de glovo y a mi me cayo un pedido de una pizzeria y yo me lo tuve que ir y me lo lleve conmigo y despues de 15 minutos yo cuando abro para comer me lo habian  hecho 2 chicken burger normal que valen 1 EU eso no es justo me quede sin comer tuve que tirar como yo tenia un pedido tuviera que ir a entregar y no podia volver te lo juro si yo estaria cerca yo volveria
review_translated_text: The code of my order was 030, look, I had ordered a chicken mayo worth EU1.30 and a cheeseburger that costs EU1.40. I am a Glovo delivery person and I received an order from a pizzeria and I had to go and take it with me and after 15 minutes when I opened to eat they had made me 2 normal chicken burgers that cost EU1. That's not fair. I was left without eating, I had to throw it away. Since I had an order, I had to go and deliver it and I couldn't go back. I swear if I were close I would come back.

name: Ana maria Caballero Perez
review_text: Buen local y limpio volveremos
review_translated_text: Nice and clean place, we'll be back

name: Luis Pintor
review_text: Hoy como muchos domingo pedimos globo con vosotros aparte de que os olvidasteis de poner una hamburguesa me entregaron un Big Mac donde tendria que ir un MC pollo,el problema es el de siempre nadie va a venir a traer lo que falta no cambiar el producto, hoy otra vez en casa 1 se queda sin cenar!!!!!
review_translated_text: Today, like many Sundays, we ordered a balloon with you, apart from the fact that you forgot to put a hamburger, they gave me a Big Mac where a MC chicken should have been, the problem is the same as always, nobody is going to come to bring what is missing, not to change the product, today again at home 1 is left without dinner!!!!!

name: marisol alcalde garza
review_text: Menos maquinaria y mas personal
review_translated_text: Less machinery and more personnel

name: Anorfin delfin
review_text: pongo una estrella porque no hay cero
review_translated_text: I'm giving one star because there's no zero.

name: Gaby Cisnero
review_text: Atencion eficiente
review_translated_text: Efficient care

name: Nura Pinto Anid
review_text:
Le pongo una estrella porque no me deja menos.
Servicio lento, se confunden en los pedidos y ademas estan muy mal organizados.
Despues de 20' esperando mi pedido que era solamente una hamburguesa y unas patatas, lo he cancelado y he puesto una reclamacion. Menos mal que lo llaman "comida rapida ". He perdido el rato y me he tenido que marchar sin la comida.
review_translated_text:
I'm giving it one star because it doesn't leave me with less.
Slow service, they mix up orders, and they're also very poorly organized.
After 20 minutes waiting for my order, which was just a burger and fries, I canceled it and filed a complaint. Thank goodness they call it "fast food." I wasted my time and had to leave without the food.

name: Sebastian Banzi
review_text:
Un desastre personal mal educando irrespetuoso con soberbia y mal talante con respecto a la comunicacion con el cliente

Solo por pedir un cambio y mostaza recibi a un mal educado hablarme con prepotencia

No vuelvo nunca mas ni porque sea el ultimo lugar para comer en Barcelona
review_translated_text:
A complete disaster. Ill-mannered, disrespectful, arrogant, and rude to customers.

Just for asking for a change and mustard, I was met with a rude and arrogant attitude.

I will never return, not even if it's the last place to eat in Barcelona.

name: Emerson Lucas Milan
review_text: Bien limpio, perfecto
review_translated_text: Very clean, perfect

name: Ratih S_ GriyaArtaTriwedari
review_text: Clean and easy to order..however sometimes we need to re check our order to make sure it has completed

name: Romel Leon
review_text: Esta bien, es dificil aparcar en la calle, pero hay un parking  cerca, la atencion bien, los banos limpios y de resto como todos los mc donald, 2 plantas, no estaba concurrido cuando fui
review_translated_text: It's okay, street parking is difficult, but there's a parking lot nearby. The service is good, the restrooms are clean, and otherwise it's like all McDonald's. It has two floors and wasn't crowded when I went.

name: Hugo Doring
review_text: Found a dirty plastic bag in my food

name: sandra muntadas
review_text: No em va agradar molt lents i a sobre es van equivocar amb la comanda.
review_translated_text: I didn't like how slow they were and on top of that they made a mistake with the order.

name: Raul Gonzalez
review_text: Lento
review_translated_text: Slow

name: Josue Bragado Covarrubias
review_text: como  siempre buen trato y buen servicio
review_translated_text: As always, good treatment and good service

name: Ismael Gallardo
review_text: Pocas mesas y banos arriba.
review_translated_text: Few tables and bathrooms upstairs.

name: Luca Pedro
review_text: Muy mal el servicio de calle Villaroel, gente que entra con patinetes y bicicletas. Que asco de sitio han diventado los McDonald's
review_translated_text: The service on Villaroel Street is terrible. People are coming in on scooters and bicycles. What a disgusting place McDonald's has transformed.

name: Philipp Dormeier
review_text: An sich ok, aber Sonderwunsche an den Burgern wurden nicht beachtet.
review_translated_text: It was okay in itself, but special requests regarding the burgers were ignored.

name: Ramon Simon
review_text: Buen sitio para tomar  hamburguesas  gran surtido de variedades cola, ect amabilidad en el servicio

review_text:
Es un sitio impresionante, nunca me imagine que seria posible preparar una hamburguesa tan mala como la que me comi hoy.

La carne mas parecia un trozo de carton, el queso daba asco al mirar, el bacon que en teoria deberia acompanar, inexistente; las papas fritas tan blandas que mas parecian papas cocidas, el pan... Mejor ni comentar

Solo ha valido la pena para recordarme que hay miles de restaurantes en Barcelona mejores que esta desgracia. Pero espero no haber contraido una infeccion alimentaria para descubrir algo tan obvio
review_translated_text:
It's an impressive place. I never imagined it would be possible to make a burger as bad as the one I ate today.

The meat looked more like a piece of cardboard; the cheese was disgusting to look at; the bacon that was supposed to accompany it was nonexistent; the fries were so soft they looked more like boiled potatoes; the bun... I'd rather not comment.

It was only worth it to remind me that there are thousands of restaurants in Barcelona that are better than this disgrace. But I hope I haven't contracted a foodborne illness by discovering something so obvious.

review_text:
Un sitio bien ubicado pero los empleados son unos sin verguenzas, sin ganas de trabajar, no tratan bien a la gente sobre todo no presentan bien las hamburguesas para llevar y no las envuelven bien, practicamente las ves que las tiran delante del mostrador. Ya esta es la tercera vez que me pasa. Hoy 16/2 a las 20:30 he ido a comprar para llevar y la chica tras darme la bolsa, la reclamaron el resto de los trabajadores de la ausencia de una de mis hamburguesas.
Tras esto, ella cogio la hamburguesa totalmente desenvuelta hablando y la metio dentro de la bolsa tal cual, sin envolver bien.
Tras yo tener la bolsa, revise que no me faltase ningun pedido, y vi que las hamburguesas se encontraban todas mal colocadas y salidas de sus envoltorios mezcladas con las patatas las cuales estaban volcadas.
Ya no vuelvo mas a comprar a este sitio.
review_translated_text:
The place is well-located, but the employees are shameless, unmotivated, and don't treat people well. They especially don't present the takeaway burgers properly and don't wrap them well; you practically see them throwing them on the counter. This is the third time this has happened to me. Today, February 16th, at 8:30 PM, I went to order takeout, and after the girl gave me the bag, the other employees complained that one of my burgers was missing.

After this, she took the completely unwrapped burger, still talking, and put it in the bag as is, without wrapping it properly.
After I got the bag, I checked to make sure nothing was missing from my order, and I saw that the burgers were all jumbled up and out of their wrappers, mixed in with the fries, which were spilled over. I will never buy from this place again.

os recomiendo no ir a este mcdonald, la chica que estaba atendiendo, aparte de saturarse con 3 pedidos, es un poco faltona y chulesca.

resumiendo que no vuelvo ahi.
a los encargados de ese mcdonald os recomiendo reconocer a la empleada que estaba hoy en la puerta.

review_translated_text:
I recommend you don't go to this McDonald's. The girl serving, aside from overloading me with three orders, is a bit rude and arrogant.
And even when I tried to talk to her, she started raising her voice in front of the delivery drivers, leaving me feeling embarrassed.
In short, I won't be going back there.
To the managers of that McDonald's, I recommend you recognize the employee who was at the door today.
And for my part, I'd like to tell her that there are dating places where she can relieve the agony and anguish she's carrying and take it out on us, the public.

Not to mention that the McFlurry with its ++ toppings was a bland ice cream with hardly any substance. I don't know... Los nuggets estan buenisimos!! Y la limpieza del sitio es aseptable.

review_text: Muy mal y muy poca educacion los del MacDonald Carrer de Villarroel, 189, 08036 Barcelona. Pedimos cena a las 23:56 y nos la cocinan cuando estabamos a mitad de cenar apagaron las luces y echaron a la calle a todo el mundo, habiamos 3 mesas. Eran las 12:15 y nos tuvimos que comer las hamburguesas en la calle, los empleados decian que no les pagaban lss horas Extras y que cobraban menos horas de las que trabajaban
review_translated_text: Very bad and very rude from the McDonald's at Carrer de Villarroel, 189, 08036 Barcelona. We ordered dinner at 11:56 pm and they cooked it for us. When we were halfway through eating, they turned off the lights and kicked everyone out onto the street. There were only three of us. It was 12:15 pm and we had to eat our burgers on the street. The employees said they weren't paid overtime and that they were paid less hours than they worked.

review_translated_text: I found the customer service extremely unprofessional when paying or asking questions. The supposed Argentinian manager was very unpleasant and, to top it off, was dressed in street clothes. He spoke rudely to my partner, trying to act superior when he had no right to respond that way. My experience at this restaurant was very unpleasant. I will never return to this McDonald's.

Lo peor de todo a sido estar haciendo cola y que fueran sacando las bolsas de basura a puerta abierta cuando en un principio deve hacerse al cierre del local y a puerta cerrada.
review_translated_text: Although the place is nice and smells clean, the kitchen staff weren't wearing hairnets to prevent hair from falling into the food, nor were they wearing gloves or their uniforms were improperly fitted, giving an impression of carelessness and poor hygiene. The worst part was having to queue and then having the garbage bags put out with the door open, when it should have been done at closing time and behind closed doors.

As embalagens sao requintadas, descartaveis e claro, mas praticas! A decoracao da lanchonete e muito depre, estilo pichacao. Os hamburgueres estavam frios.
review_translated_text: The ordering screens are few and far between, and the service is very slow. The server is attentive, but the order takes a bit of a while. A highlight is the olive oil and vinegar that come with the salad. The packaging is elegant, disposable of course, but practical! The restaurant's decor is very depressing, almost graffiti-style. The hamburgers were cold.

name: Nicole Jimenez
review_text:
The service is very slow. There wasn't any line when I bought a shake. I was second to the next in line actually. Since they were moving so slowly (you could see them move inside and you can see them talking and laughing as well so I know they're not taking it very seriously), the line piled up and everyone else was waiting for their turn. I got my shake about 25 minutes later, wasting my time for a simple shake. The one in front of me didn't even have that much food on the tray when they gave it to him.

When one of the elders asked why there weren't anyone attending to the customers in the cashier, they said everyone needs to use the machines so they wanted the elderly to use the machines... no consideration. Not everyone knows how the new technologies we have. They need to understand that and help the ones who need special attention. Instead, they treated them not so nicely.

It's not ideal as a work place either when you just want to relax and do your work at the same time as you eat. The internet connection is very slow.

As summary, this is not recommendable. From past experiences as well, they leave out a lot of orders, especially if you are in a hurry and ordered for a take away. If you don't check it one by one, you might actually not get all of what you ordered.

Si antes no me hacia gracia ir ahora menos, he cambiado de opinion sobre este local; soy diabetica y cada vez que pido cocacola light, la mayoria de veces, como hoy... no la sirven sin azucar aunque dicen que si y la verdad que con tanto hielo es dificil de apreciar pero mi medidor de azucar marca 300 desde hace 3horas y no consigo estabilizarla, aparte me encuentro mal.
otro aspecto malo es que las colas de espera son eternas por culpa de los pedidos a domicilio, se deberia gestionar de otra forma pues les dan preferencias y alguna vez he estado apunto de irme porque tenia que entrar de nuevo a trabajar.
review_translated_text:
If I wasn't keen on going before, I'm even less so now. I've changed my mind about this place. I'm diabetic, and every time I order Diet Coke, most of the time, like today... they don't serve it sugar-free even though they say they do. Honestly, with so much ice, it's hard to tell, but my blood sugar meter has been reading 300 for the past three hours, and I can't seem to stabilize it. Besides, I feel sick.
Another downside is that the lines are endless because of the delivery orders. They should be managed differently, as they give them priority, and I've been on the verge of leaving a few times because I had to go back to work.

I placed my order, but they didn't tell me they were closing. I sat down to eat, and three minutes into my meal, they kicked me out of the restaurant because they were closing. They made me leave with my food already started.

name: Juan Alvarez Porto
review_text:
Cada vez que pedimos McDonalds (siempre al mismo establecimiento) a traves de Glovo (la app de servicio a domicilio) se dejan algo. Siempre.

A la hora de reclamar, Glovo te dice que los gloveros (los que te traen el pedido a casa) no pueden abrir el paquete una vez entregado (si bien podrian cerciorarse de que esta todo bien a la hora de servirles el pedido); y McDonalds, por su parte, te dice que una vez sale el pedido del restaurante, ya no es cosa suya (pero el fallo, evidentemente, ya lo han hecho).

Asi que, como siempre, los que nos jodemos somos los usuarios. Pero nunca mas.

Insisto: los que siempre se dejan algo son los del McDonalds.

PD: Mencion a parte el tema del ketchup: que alguien me diga cual es la clave para que te pongan mas de un sobrecito.
review_translated_text:
Every time we order McDonald's (always from the same establishment) through Glovo (the delivery app), they leave something behind. Always.

When you complain, Glovo tells you that the gloveros (the ones who bring the order to your home) can't open the package once it's delivered (although they could make sure everything is okay when they serve it); and McDonald's, for its part, tells you that once the order leaves the restaurant, it's no longer their fault (but the mistake, obviously, has already been made).

So, as always, we users are the ones who get screwed. But never again.

I insist: the ones who always leave something behind are the McDonald's people.

P.S.: A separate mention of the ketchup issue: someone please tell me the key to getting more than one packet.

After reading other reviews, I was debating whether I should give one to them, but I couldn't bring myself to give them two.
Looking at the receipt and coupon, two deluxe Big Macs and one four-pack cost 14.60, but it's only 15 cents different from 14.75. I don't understand why there's such a difference in cost when the bag or size hasn't changed.
Maybe it's because there aren't enough employees... The processing was slow.
The burgers also felt a bit dry.
I don't know about other locations, but I don't think I'll go here again.

review_text: Si buscas hamburguesas Congeladas y sin hacer, algo que no pediste o un cargo por un complemento que no marcaste, definitivamente  este es tu Macdonald s, sin dudas la peor sucursal atendida, cada vez que paso por urgencia me decepcionan mas.  Mi consejo es reemplazar personal humano por monos. Que ellos atenderan de manera mas eficaz y sin marear al cliente con escusas. Por que si algo se, es que al cobrar mi dinero estaba en su punto. Soy cliente eventual hace 17 anos , y desde que cerraron el club ronald  esta empresa  podria bien dedicarse a la fontaneria. Que tengan buen dia y espero mi resena sea de vuestro agrado tanto como el servicio que me han prestado.
review_translated_text: If you're looking for frozen, undercooked burgers, something you didn't order, or a charge for an extra you didn't select, this is definitely your McDonald's. It's without a doubt the worst branch served. Every time I go to the emergency room, they disappoint me more. My advice is to replace human staff with monkeys. They'll serve customers more efficiently and without bothering them with excuses. Because if I know one thing, it's that when I got my money, it was on the money. I've been a regular customer for 17 years, and since they closed Club Ronald, this company could very well be a plumber. Have a nice day, and I hope you like my review as much as the service I received.

name: Joan Vives
review_text: Servicio pesimo, las verdad que las empleadas son francamente desagradables, por no decir peor. Sin poder identificarlas por que no llevan chapa, he presenciado como se metian con una cliente vino a reclamar que le faltaba salsa con su pedido en el mostrador, la trataron de "amargada de la vida" a sus espaldas... Mi amigo y yo nos pedimos un big mac, frio y duro, ya fuera de consumo. No me atrevi a reclamar por no querer enfrentarme al personal. No volvere mas.
review_translated_text: Terrible service. Honestly, the employees are downright unpleasant, to say the least. I couldn't identify them because they didn't have badges. I witnessed them harassing a customer who came to the counter to complain about missing sauce with her order. They called her "a bitch" behind her back. My friend and I ordered a Big Mac, which was cold and tough, already out of date. I didn't dare complain because I didn't want to confront the staff. I won't be back.

name: Israel Blazquez
review_text:
Es agradable ver una excelente atencion al cliente. Rapidez a la hora de preparar el pedido y con una buena sonrisa y actitud servicial hacia el cliente.
No estaria mal que mejorasen el filtro de contratacion en muchos otros restaurantes de esta cadena para instar al cliente a volver, no por el producto en si, sino por el trato recibido.
review_translated_text:
It's great to see such excellent customer service. They're quick to prepare the order and greet customers with a friendly smile and helpful attitude.
It would be beneficial if they improved their hiring process in many other restaurants in this chain to encourage customers to return, not for the food itself, but for the service they receive.

review_translated_text: I was pleasantly surprised. When you think of McDonald's, you think of something simple or dirty. This one, on the other hand, is very well maintained, and they serve customers perfectly and quickly.

review_text: Tot

name: Bruno Travelletti
review_text: Pesimo servicio. He pedido 4 desayunos para llevar, y me han dado 2 y a los 15 minutos los otros dos, habiendose enfriado los primeros al punto ser incomibles. Me han dicho que me darian todos frescos, y a los 10 minutos de esta nueva espera, me han dicho que no habia mas desayunos, tardando 5 minutos mas en devolverme mi dinero. Nunca mas ire a uno, ni comida rapida, ni buen servicio (le habia reclamado al chico que me mantenga caliente el desayuno, cosa que no hizo)
review_translated_text: Terrible service. I ordered four breakfasts to go, and they gave me two, then 15 minutes later the other two, by which time the first two had cooled down to the point of being inedible. They told me they would give me fresh ones, and after another 10 minutes of waiting, they told me they were out of breakfasts, taking another 5 minutes to refund my money. I will never go to one of these places again; it's not fast food, and the service is terrible (I had asked the guy to keep my breakfast warm, which he didn't do).
